[
{ type: install
  message: <<EOM
ArcadeDB installed.

Configuration files: /var/db/arcadedb/config/
Data directory: /var/db/arcadedb/databases/

Setup root password:
  mkdir -p %%PREFIX%%/etc/arcadedb
  printf "yourpassword" > %%PREFIX%%/etc/arcadedb/rootpassword
  chown arcadedb:arcadedb %%PREFIX%%/etc/arcadedb/rootpassword
  chmod 400 %%PREFIX%%/etc/arcadedb/rootpassword

Note: The password file is only read on first start. To change the password
later, stop the service, remove /var/db/arcadedb/config/server-users.jsonl,
update the password file, and restart the service.

To start ArcadeDB:
  1. Enable: sysrc arcadedb_enable=YES
  2. Start: service arcadedb start

Web console: http://localhost:2480
EOM
}
]
